The following files and directories should be added into the directory tests/testdata to be able to run all tests:

- ftp://ftp.cdc.noaa.gov/Datasets/interp_OLR/olr.day.mean.nc directly into the tests/testdata/olr.day.mean.nc.

- All files from ftp://ftp.cdc.noaa.gov/Datasets.other/MJO/eof1/ into the subdirectory tests/testdata/OriginalOMI/eof1/
- All files from ftp://ftp.cdc.noaa.gov/Datasets.other/MJO/eof2/ into the subdirectory tests/testdata/OriginalOMI/eof2/

- https://www.esrl.noaa.gov/psd/mjo/mjoindex/omi.1x.txt (Current version that ends on August 28, 2018) into tests/testdata/OriginalOMI/omi.1x.txt
